name: New Years (Lennyi)
description:
A fun little game i made for new years, in about 3 days.

Idk why i like making rocket games, this is the third one already.

Weird that it has been 3 months since my last upload, before i was mass producing these bullshit games. Now there is just my bigger project that i have been making for like 2.5 months. 

This is just supposed to be something fun, no score, no ending, nothing like that (even if i did have those planned but this game was super boring to make)

Some bugs that i do know about :

  • Camera is laggy, idk how to fix.
  • Too many obstacles = occasional frame drops
  • Characters are sometimes a bit laggy, they might fall through the ground :D
  • Other stuff on the characters
